/**
 * Shop Icons — production-grade SVGs for shop items.
 *
 * Generated by יפיופי × מוני × רטנשן (asset library reviewed in
 * `assets-library.html`). Uses `react-native-svg` (already in deps).
 *
 * Pattern: each icon takes optional `size` prop (default 24). Stroke widths
 * and color stops are hand-tuned — don't naïvely scale via `transform`.
 *
 * Lookup helper: `getShopSvgIcon(itemId)` — returns the right component for
 * a shop item id, or `null` if none. Used by ShopItemCard to render SVG
 * before falling back to Lottie.
 */
